{"tid":867572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube 大當機促使 Pornhub 流量上升 21%","createTime":"2018-10-18T19:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T00:37:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"299c84abfcc7e73ae1d117e834492d37265398ed","tid":867572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T19:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image-cdn.hypb.st/https%3A%2F%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F10%2Fyoutube-pornhub-traffic-effect-00.jpg?q=90&amp;w=1400&amp;cbr=1&amp;fit=max\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage-cdn.hypb.st%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fhk.hypebeast.com%252Ffiles%252F2018%252F10%252Fyoutube-pornhub-traffic-effect-00.jpg%3Fq%3D90%26w%3D1400%26cbr%3D1%26fit%3Dmax&h=b97d9609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每逢大事件發生，成人網站 Pornhub 便會發佈流量數據以利趨勢分析。昨日，在 YouTube 發生罕見的全球性大當機後，Pornhub 亦針對該時段做調查。結果不出所料，正當美東時間 9:30 pm 至10:45 pm 間，Pornhub 瀏覽量比起過往 10:00 pm 平均值高出 21%，可見有許多原 YouTube 受眾願意選擇 Pornhub 作為替代方案。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，Pornhub 也發現不少字詞在事件發生當日搜尋率暴增。有趣的是排行榜第一名為「asmr」──  中譯自發性知覺高潮反應，即所謂顱內高潮。其次則為「YouTube」，上升幅度達 183%。另外像是 pokemon、celebrity、 twitch、overwatch、halloween 等字詞也有顯著上升。參考以下圖示：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image-cdn.hypb.st/https%3A%2F%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F10%2Fpornhub_insights_yt_down_search_growth.jpg?q=90&amp;w=1090&amp;cbr=1&amp;fit=max\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage-cdn.hypb.st%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fhk.hypebeast.com%252Ffiles%252F2018%252F10%252Fpornhub_insights_yt_down_search_growth.jpg%3Fq%3D90%26w%3D1090%26cbr%3D1%26fit%3Dmax&h=d6643dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/10/youtube-pornhub-traffic-effect\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F10%2Fyoutube-pornhub-traffic-effect&d=t4r4g0Dhr8wDwtQfLOx%2BfU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=66dd00a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/10/youtube-pornhub-tra